attributes.action: Ensure disclosure of any information on UAPs & Non-Human Intelligences
attributes.additional_details:
In a United States of America congress hearing an expert witness has testified under oath about Unidentified Anomalous Phenomena (UAPs) & non-human “biologics”.
 
We believe it is critical that the UK Government ensure disclosure of any information about UAPs and Non-Human Intelligences.
attributes.background: We request that the Government of the United Kingdom initiate a process of setting up an office with public oversight for the disclosure of any data, documents, images and videos information relevant to Unidentified Anomalous Phenomena (UAPs) & Non-Human Intelligences.
